{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"50301-amma-how-do-you-make-ghee","title":"Amma, How Do You Make Ghee?","description":"Teena loves ghee, especially on her favourite Puran Poli. But where does ghee come from?","language":"English","langCode":"en","isRtl":false,"level":"1","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Sandhya Taksale"],"illustrators":["Shailja Jain Chougule"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"Pratham Books","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/50301-amma-how-do-you-make-ghee"},"cover":{"card":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/725461/size3/e2b03f77a1f2932b13834b337e4bea82.jpg","large":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/725461/size6/e2b03f77a1f2932b13834b337e4bea82.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/87380/size6/f25ff343a323efe3604c4480c1a13efc.jpg","text":"Teena loves ghee on her Puran Poli.\n“Amma, how do we get \npure and fresh ghee?”\n“From soft and white butter.”","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/87381/size6/07301925b9d8a215b9421c0d474226d4.jpg","text":"“And how do we get butter?”\n“By churning sweet and sour curd.”","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/87382/size6/9ba7f419bc91641ed05ddd7696ac75b0.jpg","text":"“And how do we get curd?”\n“From rich and creamy milk.”","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/87383/size6/b2690fc9230746204ff29dcf3d1169dd.jpg","text":"“And how do we get milk?”\n“Kapila, our cow, gives us milk.”","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/87384/size6/eec53bee1ddd9a2e1e7705ca0943ee19.jpg","text":"“Why does she give us milk?”\n“We give her grass and lots of love.”","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/87385/size6/a0429915dc24ebff8aa9e095a40970f6.jpg","text":"“Then?”\n“We get milk and you get ghee\nthat is pure and fresh.”","words":null},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/87386/size6/998d57676193993b4597c92c2eaf711e.jpg","text":"A kitchen is like a science laboratory. Many physical and chemical changes take place when we cook. Milk can become a lot of yummy things.\nHow do you like your milk?","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":7,"words":114}}